ugravAxulu AyuXAlu xAcukune prAMwAlanu muMxugAne gurwiMci BaxrawAxalYAlu vAtini nirvIryaM ceswunnAyi.
ilAMti eVnni caryalu wIsukuMtunnA ugraXAra AgadaM lexu.
akramaMgA BArawloki praveSiMce ugravAxulu koVxxi rojalu kASmIrlone makAM vesevAru.
ayiwe ippudu BArawloki coVrabadina ugravAxulu eVvarU kUdA akkada uMdataM lexata.
laRkare woVyibA, jERe meVhmax lAMti ugravAxa saMsWa laku ceVMxina ugravAxulu BArawloki coVrabadina veVMtane oVkka kRaNaM kUdA AlaSyaM cekuM dA xakRi«NAxi rARtrAloni surakRiwa prAMwAlaku cerukuMtunnArani kUdA grid aMcanAku vacciMxi.
coVrabAtuxArula samasyawo bAtu xeSaMlone awyaMwa kIlaka rARtramEna jammU kASmIrlo waracU jaruguwunna AMxolYanalu mariMwa aBaxrawABAvAnni rekeVwwiswunnAyi.
