DAkA ugravAxulaku sPUrwinicciMxi jakIrnAyak ane viRayaM bayataku rAvadaMwo xigvijay siMg jakIr nAyaknu poVguduwU cesina vyAKyalu wAjAgA sAmAjika mAXyamAlu bayatapeVttAyi.
xeSavyApwaMgA jakIr nAyaknu poVgidina xigvijay siMgpE vimarSala varRaM kurisiMxi. ixeMtani Ayananu mIdiyA praSniMcagA jakIrnAyaknu veVnakesukurAvadaM wappani aMgIkariMcakapogA jakIrnAyaknu cAlA maMxi kaliSArani, mareVMwo maMxi poVgidArani xigvijay siMg wananu wAnu samarXiMcukunnAru.
