aMxuvalla maMwriwva SAKa nuMci e sUcana vaccinA prawikUla vAxanalane vaswAyi.
aMxuvalla e maMwriwva SAKa kannA kUdA mAnava vanarula maMwriwva SAKa nirvahiMcadaM praswuwa kAlamAna parisWiwullo kaRtame.
vixyArXi xaSa nuMci rAjakIyAllone unna prakAS javaxekar I prawikUla aMSAlanu sAnukUlaMgA eVlA mArcukuMtAro cUdAli.
keMxra maMwrivarga viswaraNalo paxavulu kolpoyina vArikannA paxavi nilabeVttukuni kUdA SAKa mArina smqwi irAnI carcanIyAMSaMgA nilicAru.
anni viXAlugA eVMwo prAXAnyawa unna mAnava vanarula aBivqxXi maMwriwva SAKa nuMci praXAni nareMxra modI AmeVnu jOlYi maMwriwva SAKaku mArcAru.
