hExarAbAx seVMtral yUnivarsitI vixyArXi rohiw vemula Awmahawya uxaMwAnni sarigA pariRkariMcalekapoyinaMxu valla AreVseVs eVMwo AgrahaMgA uMxani aMxuvalle smqwi irAnI SAKa mArcArani maro kaWa pracAraMlo uMxi.
