I kAraNAlawone vixyAsaMsWalu wvarawigawina gurwiMpu poVMxalekapowunnAyi.
aXikArula paniwIru kAraNaMgA nANyamEna saMsWalu sEwaM gurwiMpu kosaM xIrGakAlaM nirIkRiMcAlsi vaswoMxi.
vixyAraMgaMlo niyAmakAlu, baxilIlu, vixyAsaMsWala gurwiMpu, ArWika sahakArAniki anumawulu civariki parIkRa PaliwAllo avawavakalanu pattiMcukokuMdA uMdataM ilA anniMtlonU avinIwi kanipi swoMxi.
eEsItII, yUjIsI, eVMsIE, eVnsItII vaMti niyaMwraNa saMsWala kAryakalApAllo avinIwi viSqMKalaMgA uMxane AropaNalu veVlluveVwwuwunnAyi.
