aMxuke adigiMxe wadavugA AyuXAlu aMxiswoMxi.
wirugubAtuxArulanu eVxurkoVneMxuku asax sarkArku aMga, arWabalAlanu samakUruswoMxi.
asaxnu exo oVka kAraNaMwo gaxxeV xiMci A sWAnaMlo kIluboVmmanu prawiRTiMcAlani, waxvArA paScimAsiyAlo prAbalyaM mariMwa peVMcukovAlani ameVrikA wahawahalAduwoMxi.
irAk, APGaniswAn, libiyA mAxirigA siriyApE peVwwanaM kosaM pAvulu kaxupuwoMxi.
oVkavEpu musliMla weVgala porAtaM, marovEpu agrarAjyAla aXikAra xAhaM prapaMcAnni asWiwvaMloki neVduwunnAyi.
xAruNa mAraNa kAMda prapaMca vyApwaMgA viswariMcelA ceswunnAyi.
I samasyaku pariRkAraM xoVrike avakASaM lexu.
exo oVka Sakwi wirugulenixigA rUpAMwaraM ceVMxe varakU I GarRaNa jaruguwUne uMtuMxi.
amAyakulu bali avuwUne uMtAru.
I aMSAlanniMtini baMglAxeS praXAni Rek hasInA kUdA pariSIliMcAru.
sWAnika mIdiyA A vArwalanu prawyakRa prasAraM cesi uMdakapowe cAlA varaku prANAlu nilabadevani vyAKyAniMcAru.
mIdiyA cUpina awyawsAhaM kAraNaMgA cesina prawyakRa prasArAla valla ugravAxulu eVppatikappudu jAgrawwalu wIsukuni viXvaMsaM sqRtiMcAranexi suspaRtaM.
2008lo muMbayiloni wAjmahal hotal, oVbeVrA wrideVMtlapE jarigina muRkarula xAdi saMxarBaMlo kUdA ixe viXamEna mIdiyA awyuwsAhaM apAranaRtaM weVcciMxi.
oVkavEpu ugravAxulu wAjmahal hotallo uMdi, xAdulaku pAlpaduwuMte eVlraktAnik mIdiyA A xqSyAlanu prawyakRa prasAraM cesiMxi.
polIsulu wIsukuMtunna caryalu kUdA I saMxarBaMgA mIdiyA veVlladi ceyadaMwo kasab bqMxaM eVppatikappudu vyUhAlu mArcukuMtU BaxrawA xalYAlanu muppawippalu peVttiMxi.
mIdiyA eVMwa cEwanyavaMwaMgA uMte prajAsvAmya vyavasWa aMwa patiRtaMgA unnatlu.
ayiwe miwimIrina mIdiyA cEwanyaM oVkko sAri peVnu pramAxAlaku xAriwIswuMxi.
aMxuku cAlA uxAharaNalu unnAyi.
wAjAgA baMglAxeS rAjaXAni DAkAlo jarigina ugravAxula xAdiki saMbaMXiMci kUdA mIdiyA awyuwsAhaM 20 maMxi prANAlu wIsiMxi.
koVnni sWAnika CAneVlYlu prasAraM cesina prawyakRa kaWanAlu 20 maMxi prANAlu wISAyane nijaM AlaSyaMgA veVluguloki vacciMxi.
ixi nijaMgA xuraxqRtakaramEna pariNAmame.
vixeSIyulu waracu eVkkuva saMKyalo vacce DAkAloni holI Artisan bekarI reVstAreVMtloki Exuguru sAyuXa militeVMtlu praveSiMcinappati nuMci akkadi sWAnika eVlaktAnik mIdiyA awyuwsAhaM praxarSiMciMxi.
SukravAraM rAwri woVmmixinnara gaMtala prAMwaMlo jarigina I saMGatananu sWAnika CAneVlYlu prawyakRa prasAraM ceSAyi.
I reVstAreVMtku vixeSIyulu, sWAnikaMgA panicese vixeSI xOwya sibbaMxi, maXya waragawi prajalu eVkkuvagA veVlYuwuMtAru.
patiRta Baxrawagala gulRan xOwya kAryAlayAlu aXikaMgA uMde prAMwaM.
aMxuvalla ikkada mIdiyA wama wama yUnitlawo eVppudU sixXaMgAne uMtuMxi.
ugravAxulu reVstAreVMtloniki praveSiMcagAne uppaMxukunna sWAnika mIdiyA akkada nuMci prawyakRa prasArAlu ceyadaM prAraMBiMciMxi.
reVstAreVMt kiceVnlo paniceswunna oVka kArmikudu ugravAxula nuMci wappiMcuku vacci lopali parisWiwini, eVMwa maMxi militeVMtlu unnAranna viRayAnnI polIsulaku ceVppadaM prAraMBiMcAdu.
iMkeM sWAnika mIdiyA akkadaku veVlYlipoyi awadu ceVbuwunna aMSAlanniMtini prawyakRa prasAraM cesesiMxi.
reVstAreVMtloki allA ho akbar aMtU ninAxAlu ceswU ugravAxulucoVrabaddArani A kArmikudu ceVppAdu.
wupAkulawo kAlpulu jarupuwU, bAMbulu pelcArani awadu polIsulaku weVlipAru.
jarigiMxi awanu ceVbuwuMdagA viviXa CAneVlYlu prasAraM ceseSAyi.
BaxrawA sibbaMxi wama unnawAXikArulaku samAcAraM ivvadaM, xAniki samAXAnaMgA vAru peVxxa saMKyalo balagAlanu paMpiMceMxuku AxeSAlu ivvadaM kUdA CAneVlYlalo prasAraM ayiMxi.
veVnuveVMtane BArI saMKyalo polIsulu, ryApid yAkRan beVtAliyan xalYAlu A prAMwAnni cuttumuttAyi.
ivannI prawyakRa prasAraM xvArA islAmik stet ugravAxulu wama heVd kvArtars nuMci cUsi lopalunna vAriki eVppatikappudu AxeSAlu iswU vaccArata.
eVppudEwe axanapu BaxrawAxalYAlu wamanu cuttumuduwunnAyani vAriki weVlisiMxo appati nuMci reVstAreVMtloni vArini baMxIlugA pattukovAlane AxeSAlanu islAmik stet ugravAxula heVd kvArtars nuMci vaccAyata.
xAMwo ugravAxulu vicakRaNArahiwaMgA kAlpulu jarapadaM prAraMBiMci oVka italI pOrudini, oVka arjeVMtInA pOrudini kAlci caMpAru.
ugravAxula xAdi kAraNaMgA oVka polIsu aXikAri Aspawrilo canipoyAru.
ugravAxa muRkarulu akkada xAxApu 20 maMxi vixeSIyulanu baMxIlugA pattukunnAru.
sWAnikulawo kalisi baMxIlugA 60 maMxi varakU uMdataMwo polIsulu adugu muMxuku veyalekapoyAru.
ugravAxulaku bayata jarige samAcAraM weVlisi uMdakapowe BaxrawA xalYAlu ApareRannu vijayavaMwaMgA eVlAMti prANa naRtaM lekuMdA mugiMcevAremo!
I aMSAlanniMtini baMglAxeS praXAni Rek hasInA kUdA pariSIliMcAru.
sWAnika mIdiyA A vArwalanu prawyakRa prasAraM cesi uMdakapowe cAlA varaku prANAlu nilabadevani vyAKyAniMcAru.
mIdiyA cUpina awyawsAhaM kAraNaMgA cesina prawyakRa prasArAla valla ugravAxulu eVppatikappudu jAgrawwalu wIsukuni viXvaMsaM sqRtiMcAranexi suspaRtaM.
